<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n41109d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n41" href="#n41109d">N41 (VI.B.33)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n41all.htm#n41109d"> 109(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> decapitated Turk / head under oxter / Jew or Xian under / behind</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">When <mark>a Moslem&apos;s head</mark> was struck off, in the days of the Caliphate, it was placed <mark>under his armpit</mark>, whereas that of a <mark>Jew or a Christian was set between his legs</mark>, close to the seat of dishonour. <small> Richard F. Burton, trans. <a name="RBTE3" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#RBTE3"><cite title="source">Supplemental Nights to the Book of the Thousand Nights and a Night</cite></a> (n.d.) V, 64n1</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
